Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在太强了，隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要做出让自己满意的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是...
