Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还想干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回维修站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在过去能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你要我在这里悠哉的睡觉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是，你别太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日子请等一下，今日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些人是不是疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了??
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…加贺怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们听葛雷斯说他没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他确实是没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是明天的决赛不能出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也代我这样转告风见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能视若无睹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想阻止风见吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么荒谬的车赛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能理解他吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是相信他
