Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么加贺的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情变成这样还要我坐视不管吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是为了他?
