Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到做出真正的了结为止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那是凰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是凰呀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能够赢吗?
