Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以提供给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘…
