Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:10:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你这么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直认为没做个了结就无法真正结束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那家伙有阿斯拉达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直拿这个借口来敷衍自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我没有做出了结并不是因为他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是我一直太在意风见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因为他在我输掉的墙壁的这一头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输了就到墙壁的另一头逃避他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了!不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事都不重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不到达那个终点的话我就没法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以让我继续跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论输赢我要用这台车做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么非去不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像现在这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\pos(504,705)}日本杯决胜赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和阿斯拉达不会那么简单就让你轻松超过去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不肯说吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「把冠军赢回来」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是加贺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我认识的加贺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:14:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓，反正我知道当不了明日香的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我还是喜欢隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这与明日香无关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 古德利安这么快就冲出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就超越加贺跟风见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过刚才的有点...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是第一个转弯的是加贺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一下子就超越了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是完成型路线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以锐角的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间改变行走路径
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论内线还是外线都能轻易的超车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以狭小的后照镜与探测器作判断是难以预测的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得安尼会看成两辆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这招对我已经行不通了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 比赛一开始就有白热化的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古德利安在开跑时只短暂的领先一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见与加贺一下子就超越他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是开跑时的慢动作影像吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来古德利安偷跑了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领先第一的是加贺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是风见也紧追不放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凌空漂移
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛是胜利宣言般的超车技术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我的心一直无法平静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法留在那边看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转入第二个转弯时机油漏了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人应该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是告诉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和阿斯拉达不会那么简单就让你超过的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我才是第一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两者的差距竟然是0.2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了获胜加贺拼命想抢在风见前面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 加贺又在弯道挑战了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是无法超越
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见的防备就好像铁壁一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「零的领域」的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道只能等他出错吗 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 风见依然领先
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在第二位猛追的加贺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三位是卡尔·里胥特·冯·兰德尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而从后头追上来的古德利安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经落后一圈排位第七
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我有预料到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这情况好得太不寻常了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎及驱动系统检查正在同时进行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最大的问题应该是油量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方情况应该也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推进器所消耗的油量彼此应该差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前半场要尽量少用推进器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮胎只能撑到21圈左右
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时机就由你跟隼人判断了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.22,0:19:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 领先前头的车队进入第22圈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各维修站差不多准备换轮胎了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见与加贺的差距太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进维修站的时间变得很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 风见进入维修站
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 加贺也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我就是喜欢隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与明日香无关
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心意是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排名依然不变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人的缠斗又展开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶，没有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我要一直让他领先吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰德尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己在那里碍手碍脚 怎么没注意到啊你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么非去不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像现在这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有到达终点的我是无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 这演变成白热化激斗的最终战
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下3圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见能够摆脱加贺到最后吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说加贺能反败为胜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去…赢吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说这是最后一次吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的比赛你想就这样输掉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.34,0:22:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的话一定能赢的，加贺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.87,0:22:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下3圈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.18,0:22:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变形和推进器...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的计算也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加速器最多只能再使用两次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:22:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下两次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的话一定能赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.87,0:24:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.93,0:24:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺终于超越风见了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.87,0:24:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没感觉到…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.88,0:24:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺的气息…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.75,0:24:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一圈，这是最后一圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是风见一直咬紧不放
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.40,0:24:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺能甩掉他吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.83,0:24:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要追上的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.63,0:24:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.58,0:24:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.72,0:25:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后弯道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.48,0:25:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被超了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.06,0:25:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Check Out
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.59,0:26:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的加速
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.43,0:26:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冠军是布利德·加贺
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.09,0:26:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.52,0:26:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.19,0:26:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.02,0:26:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.55,0:26:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,200)}{\pos(488.25,705)}成田机场   候机大厅
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.85,0:26:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 只打个电话给你 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.08,0:27:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.89,0:27:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于达成了愿望从赛车界引退了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.36,0:27:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来凰呀帮上你的忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.66,0:27:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢得真漂亮 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.54,0:27:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是唯一一次的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.08,0:27:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正厉害的还是他
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.37,0:27:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我也终于做了个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.14,0:27:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.48,0:27:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
